HEADWORD: Dextrality
<hw>Dex*tral"i*ty</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>The state of
being on the right-hand side; also, the quality of being right-handed;
right-handedness.</def> <rj><au>Sir T. Browne.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

